<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>深圳卫健委的微博</title><link>https://weibo.com/2831150640/</link><atom:link href="http://rsshub.app/weibo/user/2831150640" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"></atom:link><description>深圳卫健委的微博 - Made with love by RSSHub(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><generator>RSSHub</generator><webMaster>i@diygod.me (DIYgod)</webMaster><language>en</language><image><url>https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/crop.0.0.600.600.180/a8bfee30ly8hp22ftggynj20go0gomyy.jpg?KID=imgbed,tva&amp;Expires=1714288487&amp;ssig=8lYV46oPU1</url><title>深圳卫健委的微博</title><link>https://weibo.com/2831150640/</link></image><lastBuildDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 04:14:48 GMT</lastBuildDate><ttl>1</ttl><item><title>[干饭人]#长期不吃主食的人后来怎样了# 很多uu可能会为了控制体重，长期完全不吃糖，或者不吃主食，那肯定是不行的！[NO]食物中的糖分成两类：①可被人体吸收利...</title><description>&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[干饭人]&quot; src=&quot;https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/cb/2022_Foodie_org.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E9%95%BF%E6%9C%9F%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%83%E4%B8%BB%E9%A3%9F%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E5%90%8E%E6%9D%A5%E6%80%8E%E6%A0%B7%E4%BA%86%23&amp;amp;extparam=%23%E9%95%BF%E6%9C%9F%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%83%E4%B8%BB%E9%A3%9F%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E5%90%8E%E6%9D%A5%E6%80%8E%E6%A0%B7%E4%BA%86%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#长期不吃主食的人后来怎样了#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; 很多uu可能会为了控制体重，长期完全不吃糖，或者不吃主食，那肯定是不行的！&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[NO]&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/h_buyao-3a904f27f5.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;食物中的糖分成两类：&lt;br&gt;①可被人体吸收利用的有效碳水化合物（如单糖、双糖、多糖）；&lt;br&gt;②不能被消化的无效碳水化合物（如纤维素）。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;完全不摄入碳水化合物，体内一点糖分都没有，身体所需的能量得不到供应，摄入的蛋白质和脂肪也会“被迫”转化为糖类，作为能量被代谢消耗；而主食是体内碳水化合物的重要来源，如果长时间缺乏碳水化合物，会产生一系列危害：营养不良、胃肠功能紊乱、血脂代谢异常、血尿酮体升高、低血糖等等。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;中国营养学会建议，成年人每天摄入谷类200-300克，大约是一到两个拳头大，也就是每天大约2-3碗熟米饭。&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#小卫唠健康#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;（科普中国）&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;天塌了也要好好吃饭&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[馋嘴]&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_chanzui-fc1acc341b.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;。&lt;img style=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hp6ey05a4kj20hs0cvwf0.jpg&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description><link>https://weibo.com/2831150640/ObN7VBejy</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://weibo.com/2831150640/ObN7VBejy</guid><pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 04:03:27 GMT</pubDate><author>深圳卫健委</author></item><item><title>#明知景点会挤爆为何依然要出发#五一马上到，朋友圈一大波“旅游宣传片”即将来袭[跪了][跪了]利用小长假旅游，可能不是旅游，而是人类大迁徙啊，再好的身体素质...</title><description>&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%98%8E%E7%9F%A5%E6%99%AF%E7%82%B9%E4%BC%9A%E6%8C%A4%E7%88%86%E4%B8%BA%E4%BD%95%E4%BE%9D%E7%84%B6%E8%A6%81%E5%87%BA%E5%8F%91%23&amp;amp;extparam=%23%E6%98%8E%E7%9F%A5%E6%99%AF%E7%82%B9%E4%BC%9A%E6%8C%A4%E7%88%86%E4%B8%BA%E4%BD%95%E4%BE%9D%E7%84%B6%E8%A6%81%E5%87%BA%E5%8F%91%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#明知景点会挤爆为何依然要出发#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;五一马上到，朋友圈一大波“旅游宣传片”即将来袭&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[跪了]&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_guile-a8a737d3a0.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[跪了]&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_guile-a8a737d3a0.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;利用小长假旅游，可能不是旅游，而是人类大迁徙啊，再好的身体素质都扛不住在景区被挤成照片......&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;那么问题来了，五一假期你准备出去耍？还是更愿意躲在家休息？&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[doge]&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;http://t.cn/A6Tdaayp&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;width: 1rem;height: 1rem&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;网页链接&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; </description><link>https://weibo.com/2831150640/ObMOO7I83</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://weibo.com/2831150640/ObMOO7I83</guid><pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 03:16:20 GMT</pubDate><author>深圳卫健委</author></item><item><title>[费解]#真正要忌口少吃的蔬菜#？有些蔬菜，被贴上“有毒”的标签，甚至被列入了“致癌名单”......好好的蔬菜，不是被腌制就是被烧烤，被油炸，到底是谁“有毒”...</title><description>&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[费解]&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_feijie-c1df37ef03.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%9C%9F%E6%AD%A3%E8%A6%81%E5%BF%8C%E5%8F%A3%E5%B0%91%E5%90%83%E7%9A%84%E8%94%AC%E8%8F%9C%23&amp;amp;extparam=%23%E7%9C%9F%E6%AD%A3%E8%A6%81%E5%BF%8C%E5%8F%A3%E5%B0%91%E5%90%83%E7%9A%84%E8%94%AC%E8%8F%9C%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&